        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is GoBusi free to use for listing my business?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, creating a business profile on GoBusi is free. You can list your company, add details, and get discovered in the global directory without paying anything. The affiliate marketing program is also free to join—you earn commissions when you refer businesses or customers through your unique links.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does the GoBusi affiliate program work?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "GoBusi's affiliate program runs through Awin, one of the largest affiliate networks in the world. Once you join, you get unique referral links to share. Every time someone signs up or purchases through your link, you earn a commission. Awin handles all tracking, reporting, and payouts, so the system is transparent and reliable.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What types of businesses can benefit from GoBusi?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "GoBusi covers every industry and business size. It is especially valuable for small and medium businesses seeking global visibility, freelancers looking for B2B clients, affiliate marketers wanting a solid program to promote, and agencies that advise clients on growth strategies. The platform's multi-language support also makes it ideal for businesses targeting international markets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
